{"tid":1935581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【 有證據與數據：中國消失的一千四百萬人 】","createTime":"2020-03-20T16:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T16:26:12.000Z","uid":285037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4cf7a5ab84a19513b8d5a9cd0806770c7ffede71","tid":1935581,"uid":285037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T16:14:04.000Z","msg":"「香港有線新聞」做了個節目<br />\n<br />\n統計中國移動的用戶數自上月減少了725萬人<br />\n<a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/stvofbk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fstvofbk&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=c8f85ce0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/stvofbk</a><br />\n<br />\n於是有專業網友跑去查證統計<br />\n<br />\n「中國移動」移動業務本月淨增客戶數:<br />\n20年1月：-862(千戶)=-862,000<br />\n20年2月：-7,254(千戶)= -7,254,000<br />\n<br />\n資料來源 <a href=\"https://www.chinamobileltd.com/tc/ir/operation_m.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinamobileltd.com%2Ftc%2Fir%2Foperation_m.php&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=97daf4f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinamobileltd.com/tc/ir/operation_m.php</a><br />\n<br />\n中國聯通 移動出賬用戶當月淨增數：<br />\n20年1月：-1,186(千)=-1,186,000<br />\n20年2月：未有數據<br />\n1月份已經減少100萬用戶<br />\n<br />\n資料來源 <a href=\"https://www.chinaunicom.com.hk/sc/ir/operating.php?type=monthly\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinaunicom.com.hk%2Fsc%2Fir%2Foperating.php%3Ftype%3Dmonthly&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=c3ef9dfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinaunicom.com.hk/sc/ir/operating.php?type=monthly</a><br />\n<br />\n中國電訊 移動用戶數當月淨增 /減用戶數：<br />\n20年1月：+0.43(百萬戶)= +430,000<br />\n20年2月：-5.60(百萬戶)= -5,600,000<br />\n<br />\n資料來源 <a href=\"https://www.chinatelecom-h.com/sc/ir/kpi.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatelecom-h.com%2Fsc%2Fir%2Fkpi.php&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=1ce9ce16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatelecom-h.com/sc/ir/kpi.php</a><br />\n<br />\n三間電信業者龍頭<br />\n在2020年1月和2月的用戶增減數字 = -862000-7254000-1186000+430000-5600000<br />\n<br />\n= -14472000 （未計算中國聯通2月份數據）<br />\n<br />\n#總計消失1447萬行動電話用戶數<br />\n#中國辦手機必須實名認證<br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/TWNRubbish/?__tn__=C-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FTWNRubbish%2F%3F__tn__%3DC-R&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=5df602d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/TWNRubbish/?__tn__=C-R</a>"},{"pid":"8b35b0821b7c3aa6e0718527675258941c4cf08f","tid":1935581,"uid":238444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c449bf306caaec22b7327a5fafcf1b10d769bc51","tid":1935581,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T16:26:12.000Z","msg":"tui"}]}